---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="VibeWeave - 音乐情绪分析平台"
  description="通过AI技术分析音乐情绪，帮助你发现音乐背后的情感密码"
>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     HERO
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-28 md:py-36">

  <!-- Background layers -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0"
         style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 60% at 50% -10%, rgba(139,92,246,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0"
         style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 80% 80%, rgba(59,130,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 text-center">

    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="mb-8 inline-flex animate-fade-in items-center gap-2 rounded-full border px-4 py-1.5 text-sm"
         style="background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); border-color: rgba(139,92,246,0.25); color: #a78bfa;">
      <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
        <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full opacity-75"
              style="background: var(--color-vw-accent);"></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full"
              style="background: var(--color-vw-accent);"></span>
      </span>
      AI 驱动的音乐情绪分析
    </div>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h1 class="animate-fade-in delay-100 mb-6 text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl"
        style="letter-spacing: -0.03em;">
      <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa 0%, #8b5cf6 40%, #3b82f6 80%, #60a5fa 100%);
                   -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
                   background-clip: text; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 32px rgba(139,92,246,0.35));">
        感受音乐的情绪脉搏
      </span>
      <br />
      <span class="text-white">VibeWeave — 音乐情绪编织师</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Description -->
    <p class="animate-fade-in delay-200 mx-auto mb-10 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed md:text-xl"
       style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);">
      通过先进的 AI 技术分析音乐情绪，帮助你发现每首歌背后的情感密码，
      创建更符合你心情的播放列表，让音乐与情绪完美融合。
    </p>

    <!-- CTA row -->
    <div class="animate-fade-in delay-300 mx-auto flex max-w-xl flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
      <input
        type="url"
        placeholder="粘贴网易云音乐歌单链接…"
        class="h-14 flex-1 rounded-2xl border px-5 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/25 outline-none transition-colors"
        style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);"
        onfocus="this.style.borderColor='rgba(139,92,246,0.6)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 0 0 3px rgba(139,92,246,0.15)';"
        onblur="this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,0.1)'; this.style.boxShadow='none';"
      />
      <a
        href="/dashboard"
        class="inline-flex h-14 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl px-7 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl"
        style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-vw-accent), #3b82f6);
               box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(139,92,246,0.35);"
        onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 32px rgba(139,92,246,0.5)';"
        onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 20px rgba(139,92,246,0.35)';"
      >
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
        </svg>
        开始分析
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Secondary link -->
    <div class="animate-fade-in delay-400 mt-5">
      <a
        href="#features"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm transition-colors duration-150"
        style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);"
        onmouseover="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.7)';"
        onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.35)';"
      >
        了解更多
        <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     FEATURES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="features" class="relative py-24"
         style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">

    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="mb-14 text-center">
      <span class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3.5 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider"
            style="background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); border-color: rgba(139,92,246,0.2); color: #a78bfa;">
        核心功能
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-4xl"
          style="letter-spacing: -0.025em;">
        探索音乐的情感世界
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed"
         style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);">
        利用 AI 技术，深入分析音乐的情绪特征，为你提供全新的音乐体验
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Features grid -->
    <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      {[
        { icon: 'heart',     title: '音乐情绪分析',   desc: '基于 AI 技术，分析每首歌曲的情绪特征，涵盖快乐、悲伤、愤怒、平静等多种维度。' },
        { icon: 'layers',    title: '多平台歌单导入', desc: '支持网易云音乐、QQ 音乐、Spotify 等平台导入，一键分析全部歌曲。' },
        { icon: 'chart',     title: '情绪可视化',     desc: '通过直观的图表与色彩展示情绪分布，让你更清晰地感知音乐的情感轮廓。' },
        { icon: 'recommend', title: '智能歌单推荐',   desc: '根据情绪状态与偏好，智能匹配符合当前心情的歌曲与歌单。' },
        { icon: 'tag',       title: '情绪标签管理',   desc: '为歌曲添加自定义情绪标签，构建属于自己的情绪音乐库。' },
        { icon: 'sync',      title: '多设备同步',     desc: '在不同设备间同步歌单与分析结果，随时随地享受个性化体验。' },
      ].map((f, i) => (
        <div
          class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl"
          style={`background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); animation: fade-in-up 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1) ${i*60+100}ms both;`}
          onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(139,92,246,0.3)'; this.style.background='rgba(139,92,246,0.04)';"
          onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,0.07)'; this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,0.02)';"
        >
          <!-- Subtle top shimmer on hover -->
          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 group-hover:opacity-100"
               style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(139,92,246,0.5), transparent);"></div>

          <div class="mb-4 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border"
               style="background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); border-color: rgba(139,92,246,0.2); color: #a78bfa;">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8">
              {f.icon === 'heart'     && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />}
              {f.icon === 'layers'    && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />}
              {f.icon === 'chart'     && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />}
              {f.icon === 'recommend' && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 10h4.764a2 2 0 011.789 2.894l-3.5 7A2 2 0 0115.263 21h-4.017c-.163 0-.326-.02-.485-.06L7 20m7-10V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.095c-.5 0-.905.405-.905.905 0 .714-.211 1.412-.608 2.006L7 11v9m7-10h-2M7 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2h2.5" />}
              {f.icon === 'tag'       && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z" />}
              {f.icon === 'sync'      && <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />}
            </svg>
          </div>

          <h3 class="mb-1.5 text-[15px] font-semibold text-white">{f.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">{f.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     HOW IT WORKS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="how-it-works" class="relative py-24"
         style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24">

      <!-- Steps -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
        <span class="mb-4 inline-flex self-start items-center rounded-full border px-3.5 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider"
              style="background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); border-color: rgba(139,92,246,0.2); color: #a78bfa;">
          如何工作
        </span>
        <h2 class="mb-10 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-4xl"
            style="letter-spacing: -0.025em;">
          简单三步，<br />
          <span style="color: #a78bfa;">开启音乐情绪之旅</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
          {[
            { n: '01', title: '导入歌单',   desc: '从网易云音乐、QQ 音乐或 Spotify 导入你的歌单，或直接上传本地音乐文件。' },
            { n: '02', title: 'AI 情绪分析', desc: '我们的 AI 算法分析每首歌曲的情绪特征，生成详细的情绪报告。' },
            { n: '03', title: '探索与享受', desc: '查看情绪可视化结果，创建基于情绪的播放列表，发现音乐的情感世界。' },
          ].map((step, i) => (
            <div class="relative flex gap-5">
              <!-- Step circle + connector -->
              <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center">
                <div class="z-10 flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full text-sm font-bold text-white"
                     style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-vw-accent), #3b82f6);">
                  {i + 1}
                </div>
                {i < 2 && (
                  <div class="mt-2 w-px flex-1"
                       style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(139,92,246,0.4), transparent); min-height: 32px;"></div>
                )}
              </div>
              <!-- Text -->
              <div class="pt-1.5">
                <div class="mb-0.5 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest" style="color: rgba(139,92,246,0.6);">{step.n}</div>
                <h3 class="mb-1 text-base font-semibold text-white">{step.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">{step.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <a href="/dashboard"
           class="mt-10 inline-flex self-start items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03] hover:shadow-xl"
           style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-vw-accent), #3b82f6);
                  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(139,92,246,0.3);"
           onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 28px rgba(139,92,246,0.45)';"
           onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 16px rgba(139,92,246,0.3)';"
        >
          立即开始
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Platform support card -->
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="w-full rounded-3xl border p-8 text-center"
             style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-6 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl"
               style="background: rgba(139,92,246,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2);">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"
                 style="color: #a78bfa;">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mb-6 text-lg font-semibold text-white">支持的平台</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            {[
              { name: '网易云音乐', color: 'rgba(239,68,68,0.15)', border: 'rgba(239,68,68,0.25)', text: '#f87171' },
              { name: 'QQ 音乐',    color: 'rgba(234,179,8,0.12)',  border: 'rgba(234,179,8,0.22)',  text: '#fbbf24' },
              { name: 'Spotify',    color: 'rgba(16,185,129,0.12)', border: 'rgba(16,185,129,0.22)', text: '#34d399' },
            ].map(p => (
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2.5">
                <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border"
                     style={`background: ${p.color}; border-color: ${p.border};`}>
                  <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"
                       style={`color: ${p.text};`}>
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                      d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">{p.name}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     CTA
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="relative py-28" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0"
       style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(139,92,246,0.1) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-5 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-5xl"
        style="letter-spacing: -0.03em;">
      准备好探索音乐的<br />情感世界了吗？
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed md:text-lg"
       style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);">
      加入 VibeWeave，让 AI 帮你发现每首歌背后的情绪密码，
      创建更符合心情的播放列表。
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
      <a href="/dashboard"
         class="inline-flex h-14 items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-9 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03] hover:shadow-2xl"
         style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-vw-accent), #3b82f6);
                box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(139,92,246,0.4);"
         onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 40px rgba(139,92,246,0.55)';"
         onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='0 6px 24px rgba(139,92,246,0.4)';"
      >
        立即开始
        <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="/login"
         class="inline-flex h-14 items-center rounded-full border px-9 text-base font-medium transition-all duration-200"
         style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);"
         onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(139,92,246,0.5)'; this.style.color='#a78bfa'; this.style.background='rgba(139,92,246,0.06)';"
         onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,0.12)'; this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.6)'; this.style.background='transparent';"
      >
        登录账户
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
